      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In the question we are given 3 colors red, blue and white which are in an array and we must sort them in order. the colors 0,1,2 represent red,white and blue.\nSo our task really is to sort the array with all the 0s, then all the 1s and finally all remaining 2s.\n ",
      "fontSize": 124,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In the question we are given 3 colors red, blue and white which are in an array and we must sort them in order. the colors 0,1,2 represent red,white and blue.\nSo our task really is to sort the array with all the 0s, then all the 1s and finally all remaining 2s.\n ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HfUgkIBvJkyW_VM08amo9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2802.872856778288,
      "y": -2671.4548505490716,
      "width": 13977.7080078125,
      "height": 1240,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#6741d9",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
