      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "now i know from solving problems and because of Gemini that the theoretical limit of any comparison based sort is at best nlogn so if i am to use an in place comparison based sort that would be a good candidate but i don't know any do i? okay time to learn i guess. This is my sign to learn sorting of all types and apply it after i am done solving the \n2 problems for today i will learn like sorting comprehensively in place out of place and all to keep a few algorithms handy.",
      "fontSize": 124,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "now i know from solving problems and because of Gemini that the theoretical limit of any comparison based sort is at best nlogn so if i am to use an in place comparison based sort that would be a good candidate but i don't know any do i? okay time to learn i guess. This is my sign to learn sorting of all types and apply it after i am done solving the \n2 problems for today i will learn like sorting comprehensively in place out of place and all to keep a few algorithms handy.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Wi29W3UNj3V82qAcCR6T5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2810.7645200339903,
